AGI - He abducted the newborn son who had been entrusted by the social services and the tribunal of the Minors to the neonatal department of the hospital 'Spaziani' of Frosinone. A man, of 51 from Frosinone, was arrested by the police not without difficulty and after he had entangled against the agents a pittbul.
The man had taken the newborn son in violation of the measure issued by the Tribunal for the Minorites of Rome which had declared the cessation of parental power. After threatening a nurse, he ran away, bringing the baby with him. Immediately the manhunt identified in the center of Frosinone aboard a Minicar.
The man has given himself a high speed escape to the southerly area of Frosinone, putting in place maneuvers such as to cause danger to the circulation of other users, in an attempt to make the Flyer desist from continuing the pursuit. Then he stuck in front of a popular lodge where he recalled his molosso dog. With little difficulty the operators have slaved the animal and blocked the 51-year-old. The child had been entrusted to an acquaintance who had returned him to the neonathology department.&nbsp;

