&nbsp;
Europe was the only region to include countries classified as "good". Here the worst is Greece (88th), behind Hungary and Poland: Athens dismissed the inability to manage the scandal related to the interceptions of journalists by the secret services and the murder of the black news veteran Giorgos Karaivaz in 2021.&nbsp;

